I was listening to the last @gbuckstagram mixtape made for #diploandfriends and I realized that it would have been cool to play drums by ear on top of it. I took my drumsticks and my double pedal after a pause 1+ year long, so if you are a drummer, please don’t pay attention to some inaccuracies. I was just having fun! I hope you like it! 🥁🙏
